messages.content: Instead of getting one $1-2k laptop, with your luck it may be better to stock up with 2 or 3 M1 macbook airs for the same price and accept and be prepared for their fate of certain doom.
With a restore from time machine (everybody is backing up their computers, right?), you won't be out of a laptop for more than 30 mins. Do not discount this idea
